        <Parent_String>vermilion (pigment) [300013568], inorganic red pigment [300013535], red pigment [300013533], pigment by color [300013134], pigments [300013109], colorant (material) [300013026], materials by function [300014692], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
