    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Variable term referring to an imitation vermilion pigment composed of basic lead chromate, or a lake of synthetic red dye, such as eosin or scarlet dye, on a red base, such as red lead, orange mineral, or chrome red.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
